Class ValueEncoder<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pump.data.encoder.ValueEncoder<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ListEncoder, ValueEncoder.DirectEncoder

    public abstract class ValueEncoder<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    This converts an object to/from a serialized String representation of that object. This is similar to the Format class.
